<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - PDF Fusion</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { background-color: #e3f2fd; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .navbar-container {
      background: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin: 10px auto;
      width: 95%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .navbar-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .navbar-brand img { height: 50px; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .navbar-brand:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }
    .navbar-brand span { color: #125d98; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: #125d98;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover {
      background: #e3f2fd;
    }
    .container {
      background: white; 
      padding: 5px; 
      border-radius: 8px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
      margin-top: 20px; 
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      width: 100%; 
      max-width: 1200px;
    }
    .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 15px 0; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
    .team-card img { width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .team-card { text-align: center; padding: 25px; }
    h3 { color: #125d98; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    p { color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .btn-custom { background-color: #64b5f6; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; padding: 10px 15px; transition: 0.3s; }
    .btn-custom:hover { background-color: #42a5f5; }
    
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <div class="navbar-container">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= root_path %>">
      <img src="<%= asset_path('pdf-fusion-logo.png') %>" alt="PDF Fusion Logo">
      <span>PDF Fusion</span>
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="<%= root_path %>">Home</a>
      <a href="<%= about_path %>">About</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <div class="container">
    <h3 class="text-center mb-4">About Our Project</h3>
    <p>
      PDF Fusion is a powerful tool designed to simplify document generation by automating the creation of multiple personalized PDFs from a single contract template. It provides a default contract template, ensuring a ready-to-use format for users who need quick and consistent document generation. With default mapping, the system automatically aligns uploaded data fields with placeholders in the contract, eliminating the need for manual adjustments.
    </p>
    <p>
      Users can upload CSV files, allowing bulk data processing and seamless integration into the contract template. The multiple file generator efficiently creates customized PDFs for each entry in the dataset, ensuring accurate and large-scale document production. Once generated, users can download contracts individually or in bulk, streamlining the workflow for businesses that require efficient document automation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-center mt-5">About Our Team</h3>
    <p class="text-center">
      We are a dedicated team working on this project, and we would like to take this opportunity to thank our professor Randy Lin for his guidance and support throughout this journey. His expertise and insights have been invaluable to the success of our project.
    </p>

    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-3 team-card">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('ahmad.png') %>" alt="Muhammad Ahmad">
        <h5>Muhammad Ahmad</h5>
        <p>Team Leader</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 team-card">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('anjan.png') %>" alt="Anjan Panta">
        <h5>Anjan Panta</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 team-card">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('sujan.png') %>" alt="Sujan Thapaliya">
        <h5>Sujan Thapaliya</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 team-card">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('mostofa.png') %>" alt="Ehsanul Mostofa">
        <h5>Ehsanul Mostofa</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> PDF Fusion. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>


  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>